title: Dean Martin - The Ultimate Collection 3CD 320k (musicfromrizzo)
description:
Well folks, this is one Dean Martin collection no one of his fans, fans of great music selections should go without.

What a lovely line-up indeed! Great American and Italian American hits here.
I especially love the song "I will" and of course "You're nobody till somebody loves you" "Welcome to my world" "I'll be seeing you" and even "Fools rush in" plus "the door is still open to my heart" Then there's even some French numbers in here. And its so truly heartwarming to hear the sounds of the Irish gals I imagine in the chorus in some of the songs he sings - voices of such Christianly beauty - obviously filled with the spirit of goodness we love to cherish as decent men equally!

enjoy and please seed

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
